An art of squiggle lines to create atmospheric and eye popping designs. Each collection is hand drawn and there will never be any two that are the same- no matter how close same may look. These are not procedurally or randomly generated. Close inspection can clearly see some small mistakes, overlapping lines and skewed brush strokes. Each piece is 100% unique.
